* [[科摩多巨蜥|科摩多巨蜥]]與[[帝汶|帝汶]]島上已絕種的巨型[[巨蜥|巨蜥]]常被作為是島嶼巨型化的例子。然而，這些巨蜥的體型卻沒有牠們在[[澳洲|澳洲]]的已滅絕近親[[古巨蜥|古巨蜥]]來得大。而且化石紀錄顯示巨蜥科的物種是在澳洲演化出巨大體型後才遷移至[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]](因牠們生活的島嶼沒供牠們捕食的大型獵物)<ref name = "Hocknull">{{cite journal| last1= Turvey|first1=S T.|last2 =Hocknull|first2=S. A.|last3 =Piper|first3=P. J.|last4 =van den Bergh|first4=G. D.|last5 =Due|first5=R. A.|last6 =Morwood|first6=M. J.|last7 =Kurniawan|first7=I.| title = Dragon's Paradise Lost: Palaeobiogeography, Evolution and Extinction of the Largest-Ever Terrestrial Lizards (Varanidae)| journal = [[PLoS_ONE|PLoS ONE]] | volume = 4 | issue = 9 | pages = e7241 | date = 2009-09-30| language =  | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0007241 | pmc = 2748693 | pmid = 19789642| editor1-last = Turvey| editor1-first = Samuel T}}</ref>。因此科莫多巨蜥比起島嶼巨型化更類似於[[柯普定律_(生物学)|柯普定律]]。
* 生活在[[加拉巴哥群島|加拉巴哥群島]]、[[塞席爾|塞席爾]]、[[馬斯克林群島|馬斯克林群島]]、[[加那利群島|加那利群島]]上的{{link-en|巨龜|Giant tortoise}}也常被作為是島嶼巨型化的例子。然而在更新世時期，在[[澳洲|澳洲]]（[[卷角龜屬|卷角龜屬]]）、[[南亞|南亞]]（''{{link-en|Megalochelys}}''）、馬達加斯加（[[亞達伯拉象龜屬|亞達伯拉象龜屬]]）、[[北美洲|北美洲]]<ref name = "Hansen">{{Cite journal | last = Hansen | first = D. M. | authorlink =  | author2 = Donlan, C. J. | author3 = Griffiths, C. J. | author4 = Campbell, K. J. | title = Ecological history and latent conservation potential: large and giant tortoises as a model for taxon substitutions | journal = [[Ecography_(journal)|Ecography]] | volume = 33 | issue = 2 | pages = 272–284 | date = April 2010 | url = http://www.torreyaguardians.org/hansen-2010.pdf | doi = 10.1111/j.1600-0587.2010.06305.x | id =  | accessdate = 2012-03-02 | archive-date = 2014-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104043600/http://www.torreyaguardians.org/hansen-2010.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>（{{link-en|西方陸龜屬|Hesperotestudo}}）與[[南美洲|南美洲]]<ref name="Cione">{{Cite journal|last=Cione |first=A. L. |authorlink= |author2=Tonni, E. P. |author3=Soibelzon, L. |title=The Broken Zig-Zag: Late Cenozoic large mammal and tortoise extinction in South America |journal=Rev. Mus. Argentino Cienc. Nat., N.s. |volume=5 |issue=1 |pages=1–19 |year=2003 |url=http://www.ege.fcen.uba.ar/materias/general/Broken_ZigZagMACN_5_1_19_.pdf |issn=1514-5158 |doi= |accessdate=2011-02-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706084815/http://www.ege.fcen.uba.ar/materias/general/Broken_ZigZagMACN_5_1_19_.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-06 |df= }}</ref>（[[南美象龜屬|南美象龜屬]]，與現今[[加拉巴哥象龜|加拉巴哥象龜]]同屬<ref>Fariña, R.A., Vizcaíno, S.F. & De Iuliis, G. (2013) ''Megafauna: Giant Beasts of South America.'' Indiana University Press, 448 pages.</ref>）、以及一些島嶼<ref name = "Hansen"/>上，以及在[[上新世|上新世]]晚期的非洲<ref name = "THarrison">{{Cite book| last = Harrison| first = T.| title = Paleontology and Geology of Laetoli: Human Evolution in Context, Vol. 2: Fossil Hominins and the Associated Fauna| place = | publisher = [[Springer_Science+Business_Media|Springer Science+Business Media]]| series = Vertebrate Paleobiology and Paleoanthropology| origyear = | year = 2011| edition = | chapter = Tortoises (Chelonii, Testudinidae)| chapterurl = http://www.springerlink.com/content/v323658447487m5j/| pages = 479–503| language = | url = http://www.springerlink.com/content/978-90-481-9961-7/#section=847584&page=1| doi = 10.1007/978-90-481-9962-4_17| isbn = 978-90-481-9961-7| access-date = 2019-02-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190918184629/https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-90-481-9962-4#section=847584&page=1| archive-date = 2019-09-18| dead-url = yes}}</ref>（[[象龜屬|象龜屬]] ''Geochelone laetoliensis''<ref>Harrison, T. (2011) ''Paleontology and Geology of Laetoli: Human Evolution in Context. Volumen 2: Fossil Hominins and Associated Fauna.'' Springer Science & Business Media, 602 pages.</ref>）存在著體型更為巨大的陸龜。現在僅在島嶼上發現巨型陸龜是因為這些島嶼較晚被人類發現而使得島上的巨龜尚未因為[[過度開發|過度開發]]而絕種。

